{"word":"μαρτύρομαι","slug":"μαρτύρομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαρτύρομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μάρτυς'><el>μάρτυς</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b>Mid <i>to call to witness, attest, invoke</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:participle'>part.</a>, <el>μαρτύρομαι τυπτόμενος</el> <i>I call you to witness that</i> I am being beaten, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to call</i> one <i>to witness</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><i>to protest, asseverate</i>, <el>μ. ὅτι . .</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>μαρτύρομαι</el> <i>I protest</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}